org.eclipse.modisco.jee.ejbjar.EjbJar31
Interface AsyncMethodType

public interface AsyncMethodType

A representation of the model object 'Async Method Type'. The async-methodType element specifies that a session bean method has asynchronous invocation semantics.

The following features are supported:

  • Method Name
  • Method Params
  • Id
